      <title>中国节俭的假日游客表明复苏仍需努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-s-frugal-holiday-tourists-show-recovery-still-needs-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管整体出游人数有所增加，但在漫长的农历新年假期期间，中国游客的消费却很节俭，这突显了世界第二大经济体在试图重振信心和摆脱通货紧缩方面面临的困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-s-frugal-holiday-tourists-show-recovery-still-needs-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
