      <title>丹麦市政工人两年内达成 6.5% 的工资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/denmark-s-municipal-workers-reach-6-5-wage-deal-over-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦市政雇员与政府达成协议，同意在两年内平均加薪 6.5%，以应对通货膨胀的上升。]]></description>
